latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The year 2022 has been all about #EssarFamily. 

A quick look back at when #Essarites got together to create some magical moments! As we welcome 2023, we continue to learn, perform and engage, as one family. 

Wishing everyone a very #HappyNewYear2023

This festive season, Essar celebrated ‘Family Day’ in great style, with office spaces decked in Christmas flavour. Spouses & kids of Essarites visited Essar House, where loads of surprises & festive cheer awaited them! Here's a glimpse.

#Essar #EssarFamily #Essarites #MerryChristmas #HappyNewYear #Christmas #festiveseason #festival

Football World Cup fever in Mumbai!
#Essar is proud to be associated with India’s largest community football tournament - 12th @officialqpr South Mumbai Junior Soccer Challenger. Over 6,000 kids participated in the mega event this year.

@milinddeora, @amitbhatia100, @prashant_ruia and @my_bmc

#Essar remains committed towards decarbonising its operations & helping lead UK’s low carbon transition.

Today, how we define freedom will define our future. #India started with dreams of a billion people 75 yrs ago & will continue to grow in the next 75 yrs. We at #Essar believe in making it possible, with sustainability & strength. 
#TransformingForTomorrow #HappyIndependenceDay!

As #India completes 75 glorious years of Independence today, #Essarites celebrated #AzadiKaAmritMahotsav with great grandeur by joining the Nation’s #HarGharTiranga campaign. Prashant Ruia - Director #Essar, joined the Ruia Family to hoist the Indian flag.

#independenceday #independenceday2022 #happyindependenceday

#Education is the foundation for any growing nation. With that belief, & as part of the ongoing #EssarCares initiative, #EssarPorts & #EssarFoundation extended support to 38 children of St. Francis Orphanage. Read more : https://tinyurl.com/ku2jneju

We have #OnlyOneEarth. Let's preserve it for our future generations.

We at #Essar, are building a better tomorrow by investing in green economy & clean energy ecosystem. #TransformingForTomorrow #KalKeLiye

#EssarFoundersDay – A legacy event envisioned by Shri Shashi Ruia, bringing together the #EssarFamily year after year. 

An occasion that aligns and inspires #Essarites and their families with the group’s vision, mission, and future roadmap to #ExcelAtEssar together. 

#Watch | Highlights from the 41st chapter of #EssarFoundersDay

At #Essar, our people are at the heart of everything we do—collaborating, innovating, and shaping the future with confidence. With a shared spirit and determination, we continue to #ExcelAtEssar and achieve new milestones.

Here’s a glimpse of a special evening with the #EssarFamily and our leadership, who drive us forward!

#EssarFoundersDay

#Essar is proud to charge the future as the Platinum Sponsor at @india_energy_week 2025!

As India charts a bold path to a greener future, join us for dynamic conversations on energy transition, sustainability, and the industry's future for a #ViksitBharat.

Find us at Hall 1 | Booth E19 showcasing our initiatives as #IndiaGoesGreenHere at #IEW2025

#IndiaEnergyWeek2025

#Watch | Work is underway at our Stanlow refinery for #EETFuels turnaround event.

Here's a glimpse of the installation of the site’s largest 1,350-tonne crawler crane, with each crawler weighing 81 tonnes.

#EET #GreenBlueprint

From setting sail with bold ideas to building a greener future, the Maritime India Expo 2025 had it all!

As a Gold Sponsor, #Essar proudly showcased our commitment to innovation and sustainability in the maritime industry. From engaging with policymakers and industry leaders to highlighting our #GatewayOfGrowth vision, the event was a dynamic platform for collaboration and forward-thinking ideas.

Watch us in action and experience the energy at #MaritimeIndiaExpo2025.

#EssarAtMaritimeIndiaExpo #GreenBlueprint #ShippingIndustry #EssarPorts

Day 2 of the #GlobalMaritimeIndiaExpo begins, building on the insightful discussions from Day 1 that are shaping the future of the maritime sector. 

Visit the Essar booth to explore perspectives on the evolving industry landscape and the critical role of energy transition in driving sustainability. 

Stay tuned as our leadership participates in key discussions on building the ports of tomorrow. 

📍Hall 4 | B03, Bombay Exhibition Center, Mumbai 

#EssarAtMaritimeIndiaExpo #MaritimeIndiaExpo2025 #ShippingIndustry #EssarPorts #GreenBlueprint

#EssarAtDavos | Accelerating India’s Green Energy Future!

#EssarRenewables signs MoU with @cmomaharashtra_ to develop 2 GW of renewable energy, fueling the green mobility initiative with ₹8,000 crore investment.

The energy will drive the Electric Vehicle charging ecosystem for @blue_energy_motors & @greenline.in.

@devendra_fadnavis @followcii @worldeconomicforum 

#Essar #GreenBlueprint #RenewableEnergy #GreenMobility #EV #IndiaAtDavos #WEF25

latestPosts.caption:
A remarkable start to our time at the Maritime India Conference & Expo 2025!

We were honored to host Union Minister of Ports, Shipping, and Waterways, Shri @sarbanandasonowal ji, at the Essar stall.

Our senior management shared insights on our business plans in India & UK and he also took an immersive journey through our ports using our VR headset—bringing Essar’s vision to life in a whole new way.

#EssarAtMaritimeIndiaExpo #MaritimeIndiaExpo2025 #ShippingIndustry #EssarPorts #GreenBlueprint

#EssarAtDavos | @prashant.ruia spoke with Menaka Doshi from #Bloomberg on evolving global trade amidst geopolitical shifts, and how technology will commercially enable the inevitable transition to cleaner fuels. 

He highlighted #Essar's investments in building sustainable ecosystems for industrial decarbonisation, renewables, green mobility, biofuels, and digital infra.

@followcii @worldeconomicforum @bloombergbusiness 
 
 #IndiaAtDavos #WEF2025

If we had to sum up the #FutureMineralsForum 2025 in one word, it would be “visionary.”

As a Strategic Partner, #Essar proudly contributed to this global platform, shaping the future of the minerals industry. From showcasing our green steel vision to engaging with global leaders and policymakers, FMF 2025 was a dynamic stage for driving impactful conversations on sustainability and innovation.

Feel the energy and watch Essar in action at #FMF2025.
